  <h2>Who We Are</h2>

  <p>We're an independent Tesla repair team based in <strong>Kaunas, Lithuania</strong>, working out of the <a href="https://rrcarparts.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RR Car Parts</a> workshop — one of Europe's leading Tesla OEM parts suppliers. Every day we're hands-on with Tesla Model 3, Model Y, Model S, and Model X vehicles — from routine maintenance to full drivetrain rebuilds.</p>

  <p>We've been working on Teslas since 2018, learning through hands-on experience, Tesla service manuals, and thousands of hours of real repair work. We don't work for Tesla — we're independent mechanics who fix Teslas because we love the engineering and want to help owners save money.</p>

